      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:05:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>历峰集团旗下奢侈品在线零售商 Net-A-Porter 将退出中国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/richemont-s-online-luxury-retailer-net-a-porter-to-exit-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费支出疲软给中国这个全球第二大经济体的高端品牌运营带来越来越大的压力，历峰集团旗下的奢侈品电商平台 Yoox Net-A-Porter 决定退出中国市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/richemont-s-online-luxury-retailer-net-a-porter-to-exit-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 10:04:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
